text:
To-Toru-chan,
did you have something to eat...?
Doesn't seem like you've eaten anything, huh...
Well, I'll go to the convenience store then.

……
Oh, there are snacks if you want any...!

Oh, snacks you say?
That's guu-. Even my stomach agrees.

Huh? Ah...
I'll see you later then.

……！
I-it's not like that kind of meaning...!
I-I have some snacks with me too...!
